8:42'),(22,'USS Intrepid','Rare',3,3,9,45,102536,'Frontline Defender','When fighting Hostiles, if the Shield Health of the Intrepid is under 60% at the beginning of combat, increase Armor, Shield Deflection and Dodge of the Intrepid by 10%.',85,33,3,12000,250,100,'Complete Federation events or missions in mid Grade 3 space to unlock this ship.','2020-08-26 04:08:42','2020-08-26 04:08:42'),(23,'USS Enterprise','Epic',1,3,9,45,251379,'Giving what she\'s got','As long as the ship has Morale, the Enterprise heals the Shield Health by 5% whenever it gets hit.',100,40,4,16000,300,100,'Venture further into the galaxy to discover how to unlock this ship.','2020-08-26 04:08:42','2020-08-26 04:08:42'),(24,'USS Antares','Rare',4,3,9,45,76619,'Gas Mining Laser','The Mining Rate of Gas is increased by 70%',75,30,2,262000,4200,865,'Complete Federation events or missions in early Grade 3 space to unlock this ship.','2020-08-26 04:08:42','2020-08-26 04:08:42'),(25,'Legionary','Uncommon',3,3,9,45,185192,'Federation Killer','+30% against Federation ships.',85,19,3,1000,230,100,'Unknown how to acquire blueprints at this time.','2020-08-26 04:08:42','2020-08-26 04:08:42'),(26,'Centurion','Uncommon',1,3,9,45,53954,'Territorial','At the start of each round, when defending, the Centurion increases the Armor, Shield Deflection and Dodge of all ships and defense platforms by 8%',100,24,3,10000,230,100,'Complete Romulan events or missions in early Grade 3 space to unlock this ship.','2020-08-26 04:08:42','2020-08-26 04:08:42'),(27,'Gladius','Rare',2,3,9,45,106988,'Secret Weapon','When fighting Hostiles, if the Hull Health of the Gladius is under 40% at the beginning of combat, the Gladius immediately removes 15% of the opponent\'s Shield Health.',115,33,3,12000,250,100,'Complete Romulan events or missions in mid Grade 3 space to unlock this ship.','2020-08-26 04:08:42','2020-08-26 04:08:42'),(28,'Augur','Epic',3,3,9,45,230062,'Obliterate','As long as the opponent\'s ship is Burning, if the opponent is hit with the Obliterator weapon, the Augur removes 15% of the opponent\'s Hull Health.',85,40,3,16000,300,100,'Complete Romulan events or missions in late Grade 3 space to unlock this ship.','2020-08-26 04:08:42','2020-08-26 04:08:42'),(29,'Valkis','Rare',4,3,9,45,76961,'Crystal Mining Laser','The Mining Rate of Ore is increased by 70%',75,30,2,262000,4200,865,'Complete Romulan events or missions in early Grade 3 space to unlock this ship.','2020-08-26 04:08:42','2020-08-26 04:08:42');
